Package: textAnalyzer
Type: Package
Title: Tools for Analyzing Written Text
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Maren Renner <M.Renner@campus.lmu.de>
Maintainer: Maren Renner <M.Renner@campus.lmu.de>
Description: An R package designed for analyzing written text. It summarizes sentence-level metrics, analyze word frequency, and  the most common words using clean plots, making it easy to analyze language patterns in any type of text.
License: MIT
Encoding: UTF-8
